# Copy to `.env` and adjust if localhost binding fails (VPN, corporate proxy, port conflicts).
# Outbound tests like `curl portquiz.net:8080` do not prove anything about Docker-published
# ports on your machine — they are different paths.
#
# Pick any high unused port (e.g. 49821). Compose maps host:container to the same value.
CONTROL_PORT=59173
# Optional: base URL prepended to request paths in the control UI tests (default http://127.0.0.1).
# TEST_URL_BASE=http://127.0.0.1
#
# Optional: override path to default good/bad test paths JSON inside the container.
# DEFAULT_TEST_PATHS_FILE=/usr/local/share/default_test_paths.json
